  "text": "The connection mechanism exploited is based on computational reflection [CITATION_1] . Thanks to the use of reflection in STREGA, we manage to introduce Grid related concerns (such as resource finding, reservation and allocation) into applications that do not consider such issues. This paper is structured as follows. Next section introduces the concept of computational reflection. Section 3 describes the STREGA software architecture. Finally, conclusions are drawn in Section 4.",
